longBusinessSummary: Energy Resources of Australia Ltd operates as a uranium producer. It holds a 100% interest in the Jabiluka mineral lease. The company was founded in 1980 and is headquartered in Darwin, Australia. Energy Resources of Australia Ltd is a subsidiary of North Limited.
